         <abstract id="aspace_f76833a7749a1922717d87d6dcaf23ae">The collection consists of submission proposals and technical specifications from the five architectural firms that participated in the Harold Washington Library Center competition in Chicago in 1988. Also included are public comments and records of the Technical Review Committee.</abstract>
    
